STATE of North Carolina
v.
Sulyaman Alisla WASALAAM. No. 435P15-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. March 17, 2016. Sulyaman Alislam Waslaam, for Wasalaam, Sulyaman Alisla. Robert C. Montgomery, Special Deputy Attorney General, for State of N.C.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 12th of January 2016 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Scotland County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 17th of March 2016."
